<!-- What We Do -->
<section class="bg-light" id="what-we-do">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col text-center">
        <h2 class="section-heading">What We Do</h2>
        <h3 class="section-subheading">Media Strategy, Planning and Buying for Brand Awareness and Direct Response</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm text-center">
        <i class="fa fa-search-plus fa-4x"></i>
        <h5>Display</h5>
        <p class="text-left font-weight-bold">Programmatic and direct buy display advertising</p>
        <p class="text-left text-muted">We use MediaMath's TerminalOne, the leading demand side platform, to buy targeted impressions in a real-time bidding environment. With our experience and the MediaMath algorithm at work, we'll get the right message in front of the right audience for the right price. We supplement this programmatic display advertising with high impact direct buys to maximize your return on investment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm text-center">
        <i class="fa fa-search-minus fa-4x"></i>
        <h5>Paid Social</h5>
        <p class="text-left font-weight-bold">Amplify organic with paid social promotion</p>
        <p class="text-left text-muted">In crowded newsfeeds, organic posts only make it so far. That's where paid social comes in. We'll make the most of your social channels by amplifying your successful organic efforts and leveraging powerful targeting to reach potential new audiences. We'll also use social remarketing to integrate with the rest of your digital program.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm text-center">
        <i class="fa fa-search-plus fa-4x"></i>
        <h5>Remarketing</h5>
        <p class="text-left font-weight-bold">Reinforce your message across channels</p>
        <p class="text-left text-muted">We leverage remarketing at each stage of the conversion process. Each communication touchpoint provides an opportunity to reconnect with your prospects and serve them relevant content. We'll help you tailor creative messaging and optimize your bidding strategy to drive results at the lowest cost.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm text-center">
        <i class="fa fa-search-minus fa-4x"></i>
        <h5>Lead Generation</h5>
        <p class="text-left font-weight-bold">Deliver Qualified Leads</p>
        <p class="text-left text-muted">When it comes to lead generation, there are countless publishers and programs to choose from. We'll help you navigate the landscape to determine the right mix of placements to maximize your lead conversion rate. Our partnerships with top publishers allow us to identify the most efficient lead generation tactics. These include content syndication, webinars, email blasts, high quality lead programs, as well as customized solutions.</p>        
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm text-center">
        <i class="fa fa-search-plus fa-4x"></i>
        <h5>Search Engine Marketing</h5>
        <p class="text-left font-weight-bold">Increase your visibility in search results</p>
        <p class="text-left text-muted">We'll optimize your ad text and keywords to increase visibility in search results. We start with a competitive assessment and audit your existing campaigns to set campaign goals. We then test, implement, and test again to maximize your campaign performance. We're constantly monitoring data trends and making tweaks to achieve the most efficient bidding strategy.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm text-center">
        <i class="fa fa-search-minus fa-4x"></i>
        <h5>Analytics</h5>
        <p class="text-left font-weight-bold">Turning data into insights</p>
        <p class="text-left text-muted">We love data. That's why we have dedicated analytics experts on staff to monitor your campaign performance. But you'll never see a data dump from us. We're here to help you make sense of the numbers. Our advanced reporting tool aggregates your data across channels to give you a holistic view of your campaign. We're always monitoring and optimizing to ensure we're buying the right mix of media to achieve your KPIs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

